beer.beer_description:
A glass of Johnny Utah is as exhilarating as a bank robbery, this hazy pale ale is hopped up with Zappa and Citra. A big splash of melon, orange, apricot and papaya flavours and aromas will send your tastebuds to the 50-year storm that’s brewing inside. This fruit salad of a beer will have you coming back for seconds! “Utah, get me two”

HOPS
Zappa Citra
MALTS
Pale Medium Cara
